# Conventional Commits - Teste Avaliativo KPMG (Vaga Pleno)
# <type>[optional scope]: <description>
#
# [optional body]
#
# [optional footer(s)]
#
# Type: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, test, chore, perf, ci, build, revert
# Scope: company, email, auth, api, docker, prisma, etc.
# Description: imperative, present tense, max 50 chars, no period at end
#
# Examples:
# feat(company): add company validation endpoint
# fix(auth): resolve JWT token expiration issue
# docs(api): update swagger documentation
# refactor(email): simplify email template service
# test(company): add unit tests for company service
# chore(docker): update docker-compose configuration
# perf(database): optimize company queries with indexes
# ci(github): add automated testing workflow
#
# Breaking changes:
# feat(api): restructure company endpoints
#
# BREAKING CHANGE: Company endpoints now use /api/v2 prefix
#
# Issue references:
# Closes #123
# Fixes #456
